  she cries. Dominion chuckles as his crystal eyes seem to shimmer in the darkness. 
  He brushes the hair from his face and delivers his usual arrogant grin as the 
  flames from his hands end their existence in a smoldering display of vicious 
  power. “ God? God is love" Dominion waves away the ashes of their 
  remains. "And I do not love you”</font></p>
<p> </p>
